Halfred son of Walda, noted culinary critic, cookbook author and Hollin & Norland Deliveries chef will head a distinguished panel of judges.

Duilin son of Helm, Master Chef  and Sundering Seasic TV celebrity, whose Houses of the Dead, Minas Tirith restaurant was voted as one of the world's best by Cond? Nast Traveler, will run the competition.

